<br>
65 Monk<br>
65 Druid<br>
65 Shammy<br>
65 Mage/with 62 water pet<br>
61 Mage/with 61 air pet<br>
<br>
We seem to go most anywhere anytime and own the place. We do pick up an ench for candy and adds as required, such as the skelly tunnel in Ssra.<br>
<br>
Of course Monk pulls and tanks. Druid heals and instant evacs, Shammy slows, heals pets and dots, Mages kill. We have hunted in this group for about a year now, almost nightly, so it has become very easy. No questions are asked as all know their job and there friends abilities and weaknesses. <p>&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&quot;&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://members.rogers.com/stellarthief/Intrigue01.jpg&quot;&gt;<br>
